  "local_port": 55244,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Where can I get best quality soft contact lenses in Sydney?",
  "response": "In Sydney, you can find high-quality soft contact lenses from several reputable optometrists, optical stores, and online retailers. Here are some of the best options:\n\n### **1. Optical Stores and Optometrists**\n- **OPSM**: A well-known chain offering a wide range of contact lenses, including soft lenses from top brands. They provide professional eye exams and fitting services.\n  - Locations: Multiple stores across Sydney.\n  - Website: [www.opsm.com.au](https://www.opsm.com.au)\n\n- **Specsavers**: Offers affordable yet high-quality soft contact lenses. They also provide free eye tests for contact lens wearers.\n  - Locations: Multiple stores across Sydney.\n  - Website: [www.specsavers.com.au](https://www.specsavers.com.au)\n\n- **Bailey Nelson**: Known for stylish eyewear, they also offer a selection of soft contact lenses. Their in-store optometrists ensure a proper fit.\n  - Locations: Bondi, Surry Hills, and other suburbs.\n  - Website: [www.baileynelson.com.au](https://www.baileynelson.com.au)\n\n- **Eyecare Plus**: Independent optometrists offering personalized service and a variety of soft contact lenses.\n  - Locations: Multiple practices across Sydney.\n  - Website: [www.eyecareplus.com.au](https://www.eyecareplus.com.au)\n\n### **2. Online Retailers**\n- **Clearly**: A trusted online retailer offering a wide selection of soft contact lenses at competitive prices. They also provide virtual try-on features and quick delivery.\n  - Website: [www.clearly.com.au](https://www.clearly.com.au)\n\n- **Vision Direct**: Another reliable online store with a huge range of soft contact lenses from leading brands. They often have discounts and promotions.\n  - Website: [www.visiondirect.com.au](https://www.visiondirect.com.au)\n\n- **1-800 Contacts**: Offers a convenient online ordering system and a price match guarantee. They carry all major brands of soft contact lenses.\n  - Website: [au.contactsdirect.com](https://au.contactsdirect.com)\n\n### **3. Specialized Contact Lens Providers**\n- **City Eye Centre**: Located in Sydney CBD, they specialize in contact lenses and offer a wide range of options, including custom soft lenses for unique prescriptions.\n  - Location: 2-6 Spring Street, Sydney.\n  - Website: [www.cityeye.net.au](https://www.cityeye.net.au)\n\n- **Sydney Contact Lens Centre**: Experts in fitting all types of contact lenses, including soft lenses. They provide comprehensive eye care services.\n  - Location: Burwood.\n  - Website: [www.sydneycontactlens.com.au](https://www.sydneycontactlens.com.au)\n\n### Tips for Buying Soft Contact Lenses:\n- **Get a Prescription**: Always have an up-to-date prescription from an optometrist before purchasing.\n- **Brand Options**: Popular brands include Acuvue, Biofinity, Dailies, and Air Optix.\n- **Check for Discounts**: Look for promotions, bulk discounts, or loyalty programs.\n\nFor the best experience, visit a store or clinic for professional fitting and advice before purchasing online.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
